QuestData.Title: The Seawarden
QuestData.Description: The Seawarden made a deal with the Tidemistress. She handed us over to him like cattle.$B$BI despise that sea giant! If I were not trapped in this bubble, I would choke the life out of him with my own two hands.$B$BIf you cross his path before I get out of here, make him regret ever making a deal with the naga!
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill Seawarden Largush in Azuregale Bay.
QuestData.RewardText: I only wish that I had the chance to get to him first.$B$BBah! His body can rot in these waters for all I care.
